INSERT INTO orderbook_snapshots (
            market_id, yes_best_ask, yes_best_bid, no_best_ask, no_best_bid,
            captured_at, yes_updated_at, no_updated_at
        )
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $6, $6)
        ON CONFLICT (market_id) DO UPDATE SET
            yes_best_ask = $2,
            yes_best_bid = $3,
            no_best_ask = $4,
            no_best_bid = $5,
            captured_at = $6,
            yes_updated_at = $6,
            no_updated_at = $6
